data.description: Recently renovated ranch featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a large enclosed sunroom and porch perfect for relaxing or entertaining, and a back deck area complete with a hot tub. New LVP throughout the home with a stone floor in the sunroom and a stunning tile shower in the master bathroom. New garage doors and barn doors installed throughout, complete with a large, private backyard featuring a custom storage shed for extra space and storage. New furnace as part of an overall refresh for the home that pairs with custom kitchen cabinets and smart appliances ideal for any cooking enthusiast or family on the go. Only 20 minutes from the Atlanta airport, and even closer to shops, entertainment, and all Atlanta has to offer.
